itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson, Mat Best, Jarred Taylor, Dan Hollaway, and Asking Alexandria lead singer Danny Worsnop have a drunken day in Mexico that lead into a bender of a show in which a couple got married, Mat performs his hit songs, JT decided to use way too much 80's synthesizer, and Ross invites someone on stage to cut off his "Summer Of Swayze" hair. Bless you Mexico.
